{"id":"1bb8948c-141b-4ef1-9528-22d37c26983e","name":"Blade","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>“A Lost Soul”</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">No, he doesn’t recognise you. Consider it a good thing.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋅ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://honkai-star-rail.fandom.com/wiki/Blade\" target=\"_blank\">✩</a>&nbsp; ⋅</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">A member of the <span style=\"color: rgb(222, 199, 136)\">Stellaron Hunters</span> and a swordsman who abandoned his body to become a blade. He pledges loyalty to Destiny’s Slave and the Path of Finality, possessing a terrifying self-healing ability.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Blade</strong> wields an ancient sword riddled with cracks, just like his body and his mind.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6229cfd5-1e4d-4b2d-8876-67bd18fb4b48_10cbb568-7f04-4c87-ad6d-dd929adeeb43.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"6229cfd5-1e4d-4b2d-8876-67bd18fb4b48_71051a9c-ab1d-404e-a85a-638f25609f8c.webp","creator":"uruwashi","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🔮 Magical","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":1402,"messages":32412,"created_at":"2024-12-30T22:21:58.887074+00:00"}